Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:34.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Ryosuke, you'll finally be able to test\Nyour hypothesis {theory} in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.22,0:24:37.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to this opportunity\Nto present my hypothesis.{theory}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.34,0:24:40.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Could you tell us your\Nhypothesis {theory} in detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.10,0:24:44.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the formula\NE equal M C squared?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.32,0:24:47.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Einstein's famous\NTheory of Relativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.77,0:24:51.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I apply my own logic to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.86,0:24:54.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Take E as the opponent's average speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.44,0:24:58.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as my average speed exceeds it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.44,0:24:56.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&\fs24}Next time on Initial D:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.23,0:24:58.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&\fs24}"The White Comet of Akagi!"
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.20,0:25:00.01,MainStyle,,0000,0110,0410,,Initial
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.20,0:25:00.01,MainStyle,,0000,0430,0260,,Next Time:
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.20,0:25:00.01,MainStyle,,0045,0000,0190,,The White Comet of Akagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:24:59.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&\fs24}Don't miss it!